{"title":"魂系草原","authors":["舒洁"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":10,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"魂系草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（蒙古族）　舒洁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睡梦中走入草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走入马蹄耕耘的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听到牧人的歌声随风飘来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如那无云的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深远而凝重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，年年月月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勒勒车的轮子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我的思念里滚动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我童稚的华年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是在马背上度过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当马蹄传说般敲打四季的草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我发现　母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是提着奶桶凝望着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那视线尽头有牧羊离去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲拽着母亲默默的情思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母爱，是草原上不冻的河流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是在父亲的双眼里认识草原的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许久许久以后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我再一次回到草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还会这样说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲！我来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在以往的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我总是从你的双眼开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对真诚的人们讲起草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！睡梦中走入草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站在一条蓝蓝的河边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那如波浪般起伏的绿茵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"系着我长长的眷恋"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}